    <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <article id="post-3053" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/3053.html" rel="bookmark">PHP 设计模式系列 —— 资源库模式（Repository）</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-01-15T12:55:20+08:00">2016-01-15</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-01-15T12:55:20+08:00">2016-01-15 12:55:20</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    12445 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/3053.html#comments">
                        10 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/3053.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Respository-Design-Pattern-Uml-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/3053.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="639" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Respository-Design-Pattern-Uml-639x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、模式定义
Repository 是一个独立的层，介于领域层与数据映射层（数据访问层）之间。它的存在让领域层感觉不到数据访问层的存在，它提供一个类似集合的接口提供给领域层进行领域对象的访问。Repository 是仓库管理员，领域层需要什么东西只需告诉仓库管理员，由仓库管理员把东西拿给它，并不需要知道东西实际放在哪。

Repository 模式是架构模式，在设计架构时，才有参考...</p>
        </div>

