    <article id="post-3024" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/3024.html" rel="bookmark">PHP 设计模式系列 —— 访问者模式（Visitor）</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-01-13T12:58:30+08:00">2016-01-13</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-01-13T12:58:30+08:00">2016-01-13 12:58:30</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    4715 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/3024.html#comments">
                        3 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/3024.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Visitor-Design-Pattern-Uml-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/3024.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="531" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Visitor-Design-Pattern-Uml-531x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、模式定义
我们去银行柜台办业务，一般情况下会开几个个人业务柜台的，你去其中任何一个柜台办理都是可以的。我们的访问者模式可以很好付诸在这个场景中：对于银行柜台来说，他们是不用变化的，就是说今天和明天提供个人业务的柜台是不需要有变化的。而我们作为访问者，今天来银行可能是取消费流水，明天来银行可能是去办理手机银行业务，这些是我们访问者的操作，一直是在变化的。

访问者模式就是表示一个...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
            <p class="visible-xs">
                <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/3024.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
