    <article id="post-2935" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/2935.html" rel="bookmark">PHP 设计模式系列 —— 观察者模式（Observer）</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-01-07T12:57:16+08:00">2016-01-07</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2016-01-07T12:57:16+08:00">2016-01-07 12:57:16</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    11707 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/2935.html#comments">
                        7 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/2935.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Observer-Design-Pattern-Uml-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/2935.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="420" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Observer-Design-Pattern-Uml-420x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>1、模式定义
观察者模式有时也被称作发布/订阅模式，该模式用于为对象实现发布/订阅功能：一旦主体对象状态发生改变，与之关联的观察者对象会收到通知，并进行相应操作。

将一个系统分割成一个一些类相互协作的类有一个不好的副作用，那就是需要维护相关对象间的一致性。我们不希望为了维持一致性而使各类紧密耦合，这样会给维护、扩展和重用都带来不便。观察者就是解决这类的耦合关系的。

消息队列...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
            <p class="visible-xs">
                <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/2935.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
